'''''Star Wars: Republic''''', simply known as '''''Star Wars''''' for its first forty-five issues, was a series of comics published by [[Dark Horse Comics]]. The first issue came out on December 16, [[1998]]. It ran for 83 issues, spanning from before [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']] to after [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Starting with [[Republic 49|issue #49]], it became the main [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] comic. It was continued in the ''[[Star Wars: Dark Times]]'' series, which takes place in the early days of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], with continuous numeration from the ''Clone Wars'' series on the inside cover of each issue beginning with issue #84. Issues of ''Dark Times'' are independently numerated on the cover.

